<div class="app-card-container">
	<div class="card">
		<h1>About Me</h1>

		<hr>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-4">
				<%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "Profile Image", class: "profile-img" %>
				<div class="Skills">
					<% @skills.each do |skill| %>
						<div class="skill">
							<h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
							<div class="progress">
								<div 
									class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
									role="progress-bar"
									aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
									aria-valuemax="100"
									style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"	
								></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					<% end %>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col-md-8">
				<p>I've always had a love for computers growing up.  I remember taking an HTML class back in high school that I absolutely loved.  It's ironic that what I am doing is something that I enjoyed many years ago.  I love sports, spending time with friends and family, fishing, and anything outdoors.  My mindset on projects is to make sure that it is done correctly on the very first go around.  I ensure that it is done right before I put my name on it! </p>

				<p>
					<button
						class="btn btn-primary"
						type="button"
						data-toggle="collapse"
						data-target="#jobHistory"
						aria-expanded="false"
						aria-controls="jobHistory"
					>
						Job History
					</button>

					<button
						class="btn btn-primary"
						type="button"
						data-toggle="collapse"
						data-target="#education"
						aria-expanded="false"
						aria-controls="education"
					>
						Education
					</button>
				</p>
				<p>
					<div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
						<div class="card card-block">
							Vivint Customer Solutions Supervisor 
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							Vivint Business Analyst / Process Improvement Analyst
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							Vivint Training and Communications Liasion
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="collapse" id="education">
						<div class="card card-block">
							American Fork High School (2008)
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							UVU Computer Science (TBD)
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							BottegaTech (TBD)
						</div>
					</div>
				</p>

			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>




